    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Away To The Stars</strong> invites you to step into the shoes of Max, a survivor on a desolate Earth abandoned by humanity. With your forgotten past and newfound extraordinary abilities, embark on a mission to reshape the destiny of humanity on Gaia.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore an expansive universe with survival, combat, exploration, and personalization.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330000/extras/abc0ec85f8c667784e7a67481680a633.poster.avif?t=1769282063\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330000/extras/abc0ec85f8c667784e7a67481680a633.webm?t=1769282063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330000/extras/abc0ec85f8c667784e7a67481680a633.mp4?t=1769282063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore a Massive Universe:</strong> Traverse 1,000,000 procedurally generated planets across 5  galaxies. Each journey promises new discoveries, adventures, and challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330000/extras/c24a51fb63df2951ace577ae40097fd3.poster.avif?t=1769282063\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330000/extras/c24a51fb63df2951ace577ae40097fd3.webm?t=1769282063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330000/extras/c24a51fb63df2951ace577ae40097fd3.mp4?t=1769282063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Engage in Exciting Combat:</strong> Battle hostile forces, commandeer pirate ships, and customize your arsenal with unique procedurally generated weapons.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330000/extras/b97d3b42f0024cd8df8a4799aa6dadc9.poster.avif?t=1769282063\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330000/extras/b97d3b42f0024cd8df8a4799aa6dadc9.webm?t=1769282063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330000/extras/b97d3b42f0024cd8df8a4799aa6dadc9.mp4?t=1769282063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survival and Resource Management:</strong> Ensure your survival in an unforgiving world by managing your sleep, hunger, health, and energy levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Travel in Style:</strong> Pilot your ship across galaxies and speed through vast planetary landscapes on hover bikes.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330000/extras/9228d96fc4d60ded744b80115b5b9f1c.poster.avif?t=1769282063\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330000/extras/9228d96fc4d60ded744b80115b5b9f1c.webm?t=1769282063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330000/extras/9228d96fc4d60ded744b80115b5b9f1c.mp4?t=1769282063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock Mysteries and Obtain New Ships:</strong> Solve ancient puzzles, enhance your stats, and acquire new ships for your explorations. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shape Your Living Spaces:</strong> Settle on planets and shape your desired living spaces with creative customization options. Trade real estate based on fluctuating market trends. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330000/extras/b657f6b55624147eefe3e50fd774bc4c.poster.avif?t=1769282063\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330000/extras/b657f6b55624147eefe3e50fd774bc4c.webm?t=1769282063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330000/extras/b657f6b55624147eefe3e50fd774bc4c.mp4?t=1769282063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Biomes and Dynamic Weather:</strong> Planets have distinct biomes and weather patterns that will affect your stats' recovery.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Complex Dialog System:</strong> Engage with diverse species, each with unique stories to tell, creating meaningful connections and relationships that will help or punish you in your travels. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Personalize Your Spaceship:</strong> Customize your spaceship's interior, not only for aesthetics but also to gain an edge in off-planet combat.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Evocative Narrative:</strong> Dive into a narrative that evolves with every decision you make, a story that continues even when you fail. Get ready to rediscover humanity's potential in the distant stars. The future of Gaia lies in your hands. Are you ready for the adventure?</p></li></ul>",
